{% block content %}

  <article>

    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="post-breadcrumb">&larr; Home</a>
        <span class="blog-category">Free — No Strings Attached</span>
        <h1>Your Marketing Has Gaps. Let Us Show You Where.</h1>
        <p style="color:#ccc;margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:1.05rem;">Get a personalized marketing audit covering your website, SEO, social media, and ads. We'll tell you exactly what's working, what's not, and what to fix first.</p>

        <div class="audit-stats">
          <div class="audit-stat">
            <div class="audit-stat-num">3M+</div>
            <div class="audit-stat-label">Views Delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="audit-stat">
            <div class="audit-stat-num">3x</div>
            <div class="audit-stat-label">Revenue Growth</div>
          </div>
          <div class="audit-stat">
            <div class="audit-stat-num">2.5x</div>
            <div class="audit-stat-label">Traffic Increase</div>
          </div>
          <div class="audit-stat">
            <div class="audit-stat-num">48hr</div>
            <div class="audit-stat-label">Turnaround</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">

      <div class="audit-trust">
        <img src="/images/kevin-headshot.jpg" alt="Kevin Freeland" class="audit-trust-photo" width="52" height="52" />
        <div class="audit-trust-text">
          <strong>Personally reviewed by Kevin Freeland</strong><br>
          Every audit is reviewed by me personally — not a template, not a bot. You get real analysis from someone who's generated 3M+ views and tripled revenue for clients.
        </div>
      </div>

      <form class="contact-form" action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" id="audit-form" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
        <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="af9a5ef5-c8be-450b-8fdd-9039551baa76" />
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Free Marketing Audit Request" />
        <input type="hidden" name="redirect" value="https://freelandme.com/thank-you.html" />
        <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" />
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="John Smith" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john@yourbusiness.com" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="website">Website URL *</label>
            <input type="url" id="website" name="website" placeholder="https://yourbusiness.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(386) 555-0100" autocomplete="tel" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="business">What does your business do? *</label>
          <textarea id="business" name="business_description" rows="3" placeholder="e.g. We're a plumbing company in Orlando serving residential customers..." required></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="goals">What's your biggest marketing challenge right now?</label>
          <textarea id="goals" name="marketing_challenge" rows="3" placeholder="e.g. We're not getting enough leads, our social media isn't growing, we're wasting money on ads..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary btn-large btn-full">Get My Free Marketing Audit &rarr;</button>
        <p class="form-note">100% free. No obligation. No credit card. Report delivered within 48 hours.</p>
      </form>

      <div class="audit-urgency">
        We only take on 5 free audits per week to ensure quality. Spots fill fast.
      </div>

      <h2>What We'll Analyze</h2>

      <ul class="audit-check-list">
        <li><span class="audit-check">&#10003;</span> <div><strong>Website performance</strong> — speed, mobile experience, conversion paths, and whether your site is actually turning visitors into leads</div></li>
        <li><span class="audit-check">&#10003;</span> <div><strong>SEO health</strong> — how you rank on Google, technical issues holding you back, and keywords you should be targeting</div></li>
        <li><span class="audit-check">&#10003;</span> <div><strong>Social media presence</strong> — profile optimization, posting frequency, engagement rates, and content strategy gaps</div></li>
        <li><span class="audit-check">&#10003;</span> <div><strong>Paid advertising</strong> — if you're running ads, we'll review your targeting, copy, and spend efficiency</div></li>
        <li><span class="audit-check">&#10003;</span> <div><strong>Competitor analysis</strong> — what your top competitors are doing that you're not, and where you can beat them</div></li>
        <li><span class="audit-check">&#10003;</span> <div><strong>AI automation opportunities</strong> — specific tasks in your marketing that can be automated to save you 10+ hours a week</div></li>
      </ul>

      <div class="audit-callout-quote">
        <p>"Most agencies charge $500-$2,000 for this kind of analysis. We do it free because we believe every business owner deserves to know the truth about their marketing — before they spend another dollar."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">— Kevin Freeland, Founder</div>
      </div>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>

      <ol class="audit-steps">
        <li><div><strong>Submit your info above</strong> — takes 60 seconds. We just need your website and a bit about your business.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>We analyze everything</strong> — website, social profiles, Google presence, competitors, and automation opportunities.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>You get a personalized report</strong> — delivered to your email within 48 hours with specific findings and a prioritized action plan.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Optional: 15-minute strategy call</strong> — walk through the findings together. Ask questions. Zero pressure, zero obligation.</div></li>
      </ol>

      <div class="post-callout">
        <p><strong>Why It's Free</strong></p>
        <p>We've helped businesses 3x their revenue, double their viewership, and increase traffic by 250%. But most business owners don't even know what's broken until someone shows them. This audit does exactly that. If you want help fixing what we find, we're here. If not, the report is 100% yours to keep and act on.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is this really free?</summary>
          <p>Yes — 100% free. No credit card, no hidden fees, no strings attached. We provide the audit because it helps business owners see the full picture. If you want help implementing our recommendations, we're here. If not, the report is still yours.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How is this different from your SEO audit?</summary>
          <p>Our SEO audit focuses specifically on search engine optimization. This marketing audit covers everything — website, SEO, social media, advertising, and automation opportunities. It's a complete look at your entire marketing operation.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long does it take?</summary>
          <p>We deliver your full marketing audit within 48 hours. Most are completed the same business day.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What if I don't have a website?</summary>
          <p>That's fine — we can still audit your social media presence, Google Business Profile, and overall digital footprint. Just enter your business name instead of a URL.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Will you try to sell me something?</summary>
          <p>The audit stands on its own. We'll show you what needs fixing and how to fix it. If you want us to handle the implementation, we can discuss that — but there's zero pressure. Many businesses take our recommendations and handle things internally.</p>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="post-cta-box">
        <h3>Stop Guessing. Start Growing.</h3>
        <p>Find out exactly what's working, what's broken, and what to fix first — completely free.</p>
        <a href="#audit-form" class="btn-primary btn-large">Get My Free Marketing Audit &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </article>

{% endblock %}
